latestIgtvVideos.title: Styling a shirt-dress with @theyarnstory stole!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hello! Since, we are entering a chilly season (but not so chilly yet too) the accessory that has my heart is the Stole/Scarf and how playful we can be with them without really investing that much. 🤫 
In this particular styling, I have shown the ways in which we can cover up the loose areas of the dress in a very simple yet smart way for which you don’t even require anything apart from your hands.🖐🏼 
Trust me I still have infinite styles in my mind! Don’t get surprised if you see me style different scarves/stoles/shawls this season too because it really has become my new go-to accessory!🧣

I absolutely love how versatile your accessories are @theyarnstory ! 💫 
#stole #stylingideas #theyarnstory #waystostyle #stolesandscarves

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
